turn back 转身，回来，使回来
Even though she never turned back, she knew Tom was behind her. 虽然她没有转身，但却知道汤姆就在她身后。
They both turned back to look at the building. 他们同时转身看了看那栋楼。
You have a right to turn back if you're scared. 如果你害怕的话，可以回去。
A lot of snow is falling. Should we turn back? 正下着鹅毛大雪呢，我们要不要回去？
No, let's keep going till we get there. 不，我们得一直走到底。